LayoutNode.Content: For a piece that matches your unfettered style, add the Console Table from Project 62™ to your home. This two-shelf console table keeps things simple with clean andmodern style. Use as a sofa table to hold your books and photos, or place along the wall set up your stereo or record player and vinyl collection.1962 was a big year.Modernist design hit its peak and moved into homes across the country. And in Minnesota, Target was born - with the revolutionary idea to celebrate design for all.Project 62 embodies this legacy with a collection of modern pieces made for everyday living.
